column11: A novel A-D-A (acceptor-donor-acceptor) type non-fullerene small molecule,A201, consisting of anasymmetric thieno[1,2-b]indaceno[5,6-b0]thienothiophene (TITT) unit as middle D part and 2-(3-oxo-2,3-dihydroinden-1-ylidene) malononitrile (IC) groups as end-capped A parts

A novel A-D-A (acceptor-donor-acceptor) type non-fullerene small molecule, A201, consisting of an asymmetric thieno[1,2-b]indaceno[5,6-b′]thienothiophene (TITT) unit as middle D part and 2-(3-oxo-2,3-dihydroinden-1-ylidene) malononitrile (IC) groups as end-capped A parts was designed and synthesized.
